'''泰絲·格里森'''（Tess Gerritsen，{{bd|1953年|6月12日}}），[[美國|美國]][[小說家|小說家]]<ref>[http://www.tessgerritsen.com/blog/writers-and-secret-identities/ WRITERS AND SECRET IDENTITIES] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tessgerritsen.com/blog/writers-and-secret-identities/ |date=20140122063918 }} an essay by Tess Gerritsen posted to her blog Sunday, October 7, 2007 @ 11:45</ref>、[[醫師|醫師]]<ref>[http://www.tessgerritsen.com/bio/ BIO] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100725054635/http://www.tessgerritsen.com/bio/ |date=2010-07-25 }} from the Tess Gerritsen Official Blog</ref>。

==生平==
泰絲·格里森是華裔，畢業於[[史丹佛大學|史丹佛大學]]<ref name=Stanford>{{cite web|url=http://www.stanford.edu/dept/cultsoc-anthro/Pdf/casa%20layout7.pdf|format=PDF|title=CASA Newsletter|accessdate=January 20, 2009|year=1999|publisher=Cultural and Social Anthropology Department, Stanford University|archive-date=2013-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130926114216/http://www.stanford.edu/dept/cultsoc-anthro/Pdf/casa%20layout7.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，並取得[[加州大學舊金山分校|加州大學舊金山分校]]醫學博士學位<ref name=ChrisHigh>{{cite web|url=http://www.chrishigh.com/interviews/tess_gerritsen_interview.htm|title=Interview with Tess Gerristen 2007|accessdate=January 19, 2009|last=High|first=Chris|year=2007|publisher=Chris High|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080517112825/http://www.chrishigh.com/interviews/tess_gerritsen_interview.htm|archive-date=2008-05-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，之後[[夏威夷|夏威夷]][[檀香山|檀香山]]擔任內科醫師。

1995年，泰絲·格里森出版《[[貝納德的墮落|貝納德的墮落]]》（Harvest），首度躍居《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》暢銷排行榜。《貝納德的墮落》引發美國器官移植協調人協會（American Association of Transplant Coordinators）的強烈反彈。

小說《[[漂離的伊甸|漂離的伊甸]]》（Vanish）入圍[[愛倫坡獎|愛倫坡獎]]，並且獲得[[尼洛獎|尼洛獎]](Nero Award)年度最佳推理小說<ref name=Nero>{{cite web|url=http://www.nerowolfe.org/htm/neroaward/2004_Press_Release.htm|title=The Nero Award Press Release|accessdate=January 26, 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080405133714/http://www.nerowolfe.org/htm/neroaward/2004_Press_Release.htm|archivedate=2008年4月5日}}</ref><ref name=Edgar>{{cite web|url=http://www.fantasticfiction.co.uk/awards/edgar.htm|title=Edgar Awards|accessdate=January 26, 2009|archive-date=2015-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150201215106/http://www.fantasticfiction.co.uk/awards/edgar.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Macavity>{{cite web|url=http://www.mysteryreaders.org/macavity.html|title=Mystery Readers International's Macavity Awards|accessdate=January 26, 2009|publisher=Mystery Readers International|archive-date=2016-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604112234/http://www.mysteryreaders.org/macavity.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《外科醫生》（The Surgeon）獲得[[瑞塔文學獎|瑞塔文學獎]]。

